{"tid":982880,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都金澤白川鄉高山名古屋七日七夜點玩好?","createTime":"2019-01-15T13:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T02:10:44.000Z","uid":124623,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"925b4245b0aad22030fbe2b80cddfffafd1e260a","tid":982880,"uid":124623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"17/1 (thur)<br />\n20:10 香港terminal 2 &gt; 00:35 關西terminal 1 &gt; 住first cabin關西機場<br />\n<br />\n18/1 (fri)<br />\n拎高山北陸5日PASS &gt; 機場7:27-11:14金澤(劃位) &gt; 酒店放行李 &gt; 金澤城公園&amp;兼六園(if有雪) / 21世紀博物館 &gt; 新高岡多啦A夢空地 &gt; 加賀溫泉(山中) &gt; 富山站買蝦片 &gt; 酒店<br />\nRemarks:金澤城公園同兼六園去過,如果有雪想再去多一次,次選係去21世紀博物館,不過其實我麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n19/1 (sat)<br />\n近江町市場 &gt; 拎20號白川鄉車飛 &gt; (9:54-12:09雷鳥返京都) 鞍馬 &gt; 貴船點燈 &gt; (21:21－23:29雷鳥返金澤)(來回劃位)<br />\n<br />\n20/1 (sun)<br />\ncheck out &gt; (booked)9:10-10:35白川鄉 &gt; 搵locker放行李 &gt; 16:15/17:30離開白川鄉(No booking) &gt; 高山酒店  &gt; 燒肉<br />\n<br />\n21/1 (mon)<br />\n7:40or9:40飛驒古川 &gt; 圓光寺 &gt; 白壁土藏街 &gt; 瀨戶川 &gt; 本光寺 &gt; 氣多若宮神社 &gt; 飛驒國分寺 &gt; 高山老街 &gt; 高山陣屋<br />\n<br />\n22/1 (tue) 完pass<br />\n宮川朝市 &gt; (劃位)9:38-12:04去名古屋 &gt; 放行李first cabin &gt; 名古屋城 &gt; 名花之里<br />\n<br />\n23/1 (wed)<br />\n(booked)8:00高速巴士去京都 &gt; 10:47京都車站放行李 &gt; 住first cabin難波<br />\n<br />\n24/1 (thur)<br />\nThe Guest Caf&eacute;食比卡超 &amp; 買下水果 &gt; 13:00 南海難波-13:41機場 &gt; 15:35 terminal 1 &gt; 19:10香港<br />\n<br />\n問題1:加賀山中溫泉有冇日歸推介?<br />\n問題2:鞍馬行去貴船要幾耐到?冬天落雪行唔行到?我獨遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題3:我book唔到白川鄉去高山果程巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有非預約巴士,但如果多人到上唔到5點半尾班車會點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果日5點半要清場準備點燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題4:高山邊間燒肉平同適合一個人食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題5:22號果日下午係名古屋應該仲有d時間,做咩好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題6:23號果日諗唔到遊京都邊到好,我好鍾意京都,但大路野好多都去過,求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題7:究竟電鬚刨係咪要拆刀片放落行李,機身(應該係鋰電)要跟身hand carry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e812162d41129fd90441ce8d0468549bae123ba2","tid":982880,"uid":107023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"行程趕到pk"},{"pid":"067214b3cada6f587cd58d1ab3075266b3829ed2","tid":982880,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前都係大阪京都高山金澤 但我自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92d8dd350b36264288069884e0af0c6b67f933d","tid":982880,"uid":124623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e812162d41129fd90441ce8d0468549bae123ba2","tid":982880,"uid":107023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"行程趕到pk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"我都覺,D時間預到岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a8f005737c35bdbde7a712e511bd74cf32b8ec","tid":982880,"uid":124623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"067214b3cada6f587cd58d1ab3075266b3829ed2","tid":982880,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img